  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema625_05_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2_light_purple" lang="y">모눈을 이용하여 반지름이 5 m인 원의 넓이를 어림해 봅시다.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <div class="flex_col_box">
            <div class="img_box">
